      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. It currently suffers from significant mechanical issues, including a failing transmission and an engine that requires a complete overhaul to be roadworthy again. The exterior shows heavy wear with noticeable rust patches and faded paint, while the interior requires deep cleaning and several upholstery repairs. This is a non-running vehicle that will need to be towed, but it offers a complete frame for a dedicated restoration enthusiast.",
