    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every aspect of the car, from the flawless exterior paint to the pristine interior, has been meticulously maintained. There are no scratches, dents, or signs of wear anywhere. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history and all systems functioning exactly as they did on day one. For a buyer seeking a showroom-quality example with zero compromises, this is the ideal choice.",
      "price": 49500.0,
