      "description": "Calling all weekend mechanics and restoration enthusiasts! This vehicle is the perfect project for someone looking to get their hands dirty and bring a classic back to life. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic attention, it offers a great foundation for a full rebuild or a valuable source of parts. Grab this diamond in the rough and make it your own!",
